{"tid":911708,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【浸大塵爆】湯博士：食用粉末更易引發爆炸　用水救或有危險","createTime":"2018-11-22T06:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T06:12:16.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"83983c1fb9b801adaeb1eb2f59c446668fd34ce9","tid":911708,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T06:05:32.000Z","msg":"香港中文大學物理系高級講師湯兆昇博士指，粉末體積雖然微小，但潑灑分散，暴露於空氣時的表面積很大，只要於密閉空間內有火源，物質表面受熱氣化後，再與氧氣混合被高速燃燒時，火焰和熱力透過氣流急速傳遞，便可能引發爆炸，而其中沾米粉、麵粉、粟粉等食用粉由碳水化合物組成，因燃點相對低，被潑灑時會更容易引起爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n湯亦指當塵爆發生時，用水救火可能有危險，若水量不足，水分會被急速蒸發澎脹，進一步帶動粉末，令爆炸範圍更廣，而用風吹亦會有同樣風險，因此較適宜把火源輕輕蓋上，與空氣隔絕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181122/s00001/1542859306880?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181122%2Fs00001%2F1542859306880%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=WAA6jluBdfAnxImLkW4RQfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=2d94da4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181122%2Fs00001%2F1542859306880%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=1ab5bbc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181122/s00001/1542859306880?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"7c56a89f4c69b6b609f56f2a503def15511cb1b4","tid":911708,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"一於用粉劑滅火筒玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}